Gloves for Grief 🫶🥊🤍 

My heart goes out to anyone who has lost a child, experienced pregnancy loss, miscarriage or lost a loved one. 

Although I’m so sad we all had to meet under these circumstances I’m thankful for this community of women and families who have had these unimaginable losses and still keep going and Stay Strong and make me feel less alone in my feelings. 

Much love and thank you to everyone who came out to our 1st @glovesforgrief class and for all the generous donations and local businesses who donated products and items for our special event.

Thank you to @terrampickett and @karenbadalhacker for partnering with me on this and being such a support through this time.

Introducing the new AshleyGuarrasi.com.

@ashleyguarrasi is an absolute force to be reckoned with. And it was time for a site that matched the level she’s on.

Which honestly, is a tall order. This woman’s worked with UFC, Nike, Apple, Mercedes Benz, and countless other top fitness, tech, travel, and hospitality brands around the world.

Ashley and I knocked this out in a one-day design intensive. Design intensives are great for:
— boundary-breakers ready to collaborate and get fast results
— established biz owners who want a pro to run with their vision and check things off their design to-do list
— fresh entrepreneurs who need an impactful brand or site to get their dream going yesterday

If you’re on the verge of something great — a new business, a pivot, or some killer idea - and it’s been on the back burner… it’s time to surge forward. A design intensive is how we get it done.

Stop thinking. Stop dreaming. Inquire now @theuntamedcreative.co. Link in bio.
